These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  entrepreneur, project-manager, security-guard
1. the project-manager is on the far left##1
2. the entrepreneur is on the right of the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Job   | project-manager | security-guard | entrepreneur |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  firefighter, manager, lawyer
1. the lawyer is on the far right##1
2. the firefighter is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Job   | firefighter | manager | lawyer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, drawing, singing
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| Hobby   | gardening | drawing | singing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: british, canadian, thai
1. the canadian is on the far right##1
2. the canadian is on the right of the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Nationality   | british | thai | canadian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, lemonade
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2      |   3   |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | cola | lemonade |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-6::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, trike, motorbike
1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2  |  3   |
| Transport   | motorbike | trike | tram |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, western, musical
1. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | disaster | western |

 #################################

 
